<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Viewing Request Confirmation</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,200..1000&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: "Nunito Sans", sans-serif;
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #222222;
      }
      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      table td {
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #28a745;
        padding: 20px 5px;
        color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #28a745;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Viewing Request Confirmation</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Dear <%= user.firstname %>,</p>
        <p>
          Your request for viewing the property located at
          <strong><%= property.address %></strong> has been successfully submitted.
        </p>
        <p>Here are the details of your viewing request:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Preferred Date:</strong> <%= viewing.preferredDate %></li>
          <li><strong>Viewing Type:</strong> <%= viewing.viewingType %></li>
          <li><strong>Property Category:</strong> <%= property.category %></li>
          <li><strong>Property Price per month:</strong> Ghc <%= property.price %></li>
          <li><strong>Amenities:</strong> <%= property.amenities.map(a => a.name).join(", ") %></li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Our team will reach out to you shortly to confirm the details.
          For any questions, please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:support@irentservices.com">support@irentservices.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing iRENT Services!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          iRENT Services | Providing the best platform for property rentals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
